snippet.title: Space Orbs Complete playing on a PAL C64 with two joysticks
snippet.description:
The complete edition of Space Orbs is now available and I attempt to play two player by myself on an PAL C64 using two joysticks! Space Orbs is a co-op puzzle game in the vein of magical drop but without time pressure and with multiplayer!
The game is available to download from https://sakrac.itch.io/space-orbs
